Enron's Status of Participation in the World Energy Congress
	Enron has budgeted $150,000 for the participation in the World Energy Congress
	Enron has a reserved an exhibition space of 100 square meters 
	Enron will host one private reception for 100 key energy and political leaders and various smaller group meetings
	Enron participation is expected to be approximately 20 local, regional and international representatives

Please advise how you wish to proceed.

